label.value: protein expression-based MHC presentation evidence

value.value: A type of protein expression evidence that employs MHC molecule motif or alleles present to determine that a specific MHC molecule or class of MHC molecules presented a ligand.

label.value: specific MHC protein expression-based MHC presentation evidence

value.value: A type of protein expression-based MHC presentation evidence that employs knowledge of a single specific MHC molecule's presence to determine that a specific MHC molecule presented a ligand.

label.value: MHC:ligand binding based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of protein binding evidence that employs an assay measuring binding of an MHC molecule to a ligand to determine that T cells can recognize the ligand when presented by that MHC molecule.

label.value: MHC complex binding prediction based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of computational evidence that employs a computational tool to predict MHC complex binding to a ligand to infer that T cells can recognize the ligand when presented by that MHC molecule.

label.value: inference of MHC restriction based on shared MHC expression

value.value: A type of inferential evidence that employs the association of specific MHC molecule expression by a subject population with a T cell response to infer that T cells can recognize the ligand when presented by that MHC molecule.

label.value: T cell epitope assay type based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of direct assay evidence that employs the type of T cell epitope assay to determine that a specific ligand is restricted by a MHC molecule or class of MHC molecules.

label.value: MHC-specific blocking based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of protein binding evidence that employs the specific blocking of MHC molecules to determine that a ligand is restricted by that MHC molecule or class of MHC molecules.

label.value: specific MHC molecule based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of direct assay evidence that employs the use of a specific MHC molecule in a T cell response assay to determine that a specific ligand is restricted by that MHC molecule.

label.value: T cell type based MHC restriction evidence

value.value: A type of direct assay evidence that employs a specific T cell type (CD4+ or CD8+) to determine that a ligand is restricted by a class of MHC molecules.
